cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC 

This paper uses machine learning techniques to classify patients with Alzheimer's disease and mild cognitive impairment based on features extracted from MRI images of the hippocampus. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories.
